</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="mb-3"><label class="pm-form-label">Auto-Segmentation Rules</label>
<div class="p-2 border rounded d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-1"><span style="font-size:12px">Mark as VIP if Lifetime Value > KES 50,000</span><button class="pm-btn pm-btn-sm" type="button"><i class="bi bi-pencil"></i></button></div>
<div class="p-2 border rounded d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center"><span style="font-size:12px">Mark as Churn Risk if no payment in 90 days</span><button class="pm-btn pm-btn-sm" type="button"><i class="bi bi-pencil"></i></button></div>
</div>
</div>
