<div>
<h3 class="pm-section-title"><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-text-fill" style="color:var(--pm-primary)"></i> 3.3.1 — Invoice Creation &amp; Management</h3>
<p class="pm-section-sub">Create, send, and track professional invoices. Manage templates,
                                taxes, and multi-currency billing.</p>
</div>
<div class="d-flex gap-2" style="gap:8px">
<button (click)="openModal('p33_invoiceTemplatesModal')" class="pm-btn pm-btn-sm" type="button"><i class="bi bi-palette"></i> Templates</button>
<button (click)="openModal('p33_newInvoiceModal')" class="pm-btn pm-btn-sm pm-btn-primary" type="button"><i class="bi bi-plus-lg"></i> Create Invoice</button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="pm-tab-pills mb-3">
<button (click)="setInvoiceFilter('all', $event)" class="pm-tab-pill active" type="button">All
                            Invoices</button>
<button (click)="setInvoiceFilter('draft', $event)" class="pm-tab-pill" type="button">Drafts
                            (2)</button>
<button (click)="setInvoiceFilter('unpaid', $event)" class="pm-tab-pill" type="button">Unpaid
                            (5)</button>
<button (click)="setInvoiceFilter('paid', $event)" class="pm-tab-pill" type="button">Paid</button>
</div>
<div class="table-responsive">
