</select></div>
<div class="mb-3"><label class="pm-form-label">Approval Logic</label><select class="pm-form-control">
<option>Pause for manual approval before disbursing</option>
<option>Auto-disburse if variance < 5% from last month</option>
</select></div>
<div class="p-3 rounded" style="background:var(--pm-warning-soft);font-size:12px">Auto-payroll will
                        compile timesheets, leaves, and fixed salaries on the designated date and alert the approver.
                    </div>
